infrastructure in Rakuen was dismantled when the office closed, but intake ledgers were
transferred to sealed sections of Kel'Shadra's Interface Galleries. Rakuen has filed two formal
access requests; both remain unanswered in the same gallery. For Garden Ledger Clerks, the
Bell Synod is not historical abstraction—it is the mechanism for approximately forty documented
testimony disappearances with names attached.

